text:
After over 24 hours straight, @HouseDemocrats pulled out all the stops to fight back against the One Big, Ugly Budget Bill because it will:
 
❌Strip 17 million people off of their healthcare;
 
❌Enact the largest cuts to #Medicaid and food and nutrition services like #SNAP in history, and; 
 
❌Cause an estimated 1 in 4 nursing homes to close.
 
I voted a STRONG NO—as I promised the people of our District I would.
